### Componente: API Auth — Contratos JSON (TSK-03)

#### `POST /api/auth/login`

Request:
```json
{
  "email": "admin@pachanga.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}
```

Response 200:
```json
{
  "user": {
    "id": "uuid",
    "email": "admin@pachanga.com",
    "name": "Dueño Pachanga",
    "role": "ADMIN"
  },
  "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs..."
}
```

Response 401:
```json
{ "error": "Email o contraseña incorrectos" }
```

#### `GET /api/auth/me` (requires `Authorization: Bearer <token>`)

Response 200:
```json
{
  "id": "uuid",
  "email": "admin@pachanga.com",
  "name": "Dueño Pachanga",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}
```

Response 401:
```json
{ "error": "Token inválido o expirado" }
```

#### `GET /api/health`

Response 200:
```json
{ "status": "ok", "timestamp": "2026-02-24T23:55:48.000Z" }
```

